----

IPIX is an attorney-run enterprise that sues developers in the graphical sphere for patent infringement. Patent lawsuits are the moneymaker of IPIX.  IPIX has applied for its main patents also at the European Patent Office.  Some people are trying to raise funds to file an opposition.

